and personnel==\nCredits adapted from liner notes of 12-inch single.<ref name=\"12-inch\">{{cite AV media notes|title=What It Feels Like for a Girl|others=Madonna|year=2001|type=US 12-inch single liner notes|publisher=Maverick Records|id=9 42372-0}}</ref>\n\n===Management===\n*Recorded at [[Sarm West Studios]], [[Notting Hill]], [[London]]\n*Mixed at [[Olympic Studios]], London\n*Mastered at [[Metropolis Group|Metropolis Studios]], London\n*Webo Girl Publishing, Inc., Warner Bros. Music Corp (ASCAP), 1000 Lights Music Ltd, Warner-Tamerlane Publishing Corp. (BMI)\n\n===Personnel===\n{{div col}}\n* Madonna&nbsp;\u2013 vocals, songwriter, production\n* [[Guy Sigsworth]]&nbsp;\u2013 songwriter, production, guitar, keyboards, [[programming (music)|programming]]\n* [[Spike Stent|Mark \"Spike\" Stent]]&nbsp;\u2013 production, mixing, mastering\n* [[David Torn]]&nbsp;\u2013 songwriter\n* Kevin Reagan&nbsp;\u2013  art direction, design\n* Matthew Lindauer&nbsp;\u2013 design\n* Ray Janos&nbsp;\u2013 lacquer cut\n* [[Jean-Baptiste Mondino]]&nbsp;\u2013  photography\n* Caresse Henry&nbsp;\u2013 management\n{{div end}}\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n!scope=\"col\"|Chart (2001)\n!scope=\"col\"|Peak<br>position\n|-\n{{singlechart|Australia|6|artist=Madonna|song=What It Feels Like for a Girl|rowheader=true|accessdate=May 20, 2018|refname=\"aus\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Australiadance|1|url=http://pandora.nla.gov.au/pan/23790/20020221-0000/www.aria.com.au/issue584.PDF |urltitle=Chart Report, 7 May 2001, Issue #584|rowheader=true|accessdate=May 20, 2018|refname=\"ausdance\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Austria|26|artist=Madonna|song=What It Feels Like for a Girl|rowheader=true|accessdate=May 20, 2018|refname=\"aut\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Flanders|23|artist=Madonna|song=What It Feels Like for a Girl|rowheader=true|accessdate=May 20, 2018|refname=\"fla\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Wallonia|14|art